{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a walk-up, a fifth-floor walk-up, in the Bronx, but a large apartment, five rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were happy to be here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had very good recommendations from the American Joint Distribution Committee, because I worked as a-- as a bookkeeper, first in the Jewish committee, and then I worked in the offices of the Jewish Joint Distribution Committee.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned-- I knew-- I was a little bit familiar with the English language.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took some lessons before the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and then working under American supervision, I learned the language much better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came here equipped with recommendations from-- from them, you know, as a bookkeeper, it's also-- I was already typing and writing letters, and you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when I came here to the Jewish Joint Distribution Committee, and I showed them these papers, they said, we cannot give you a job.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're overqualified.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I couldn't get a job in any profession, so I just went to a factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked with pocketbooks In fact, I became a framer of pocketbooks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the old-type pocketbooks had frames, the way you close it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the frames had to be covered with the plastic or with the leather that the pocketbook was made of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was a special art, to frame pocketbooks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I became a framer of pocketbooks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I make $0.75 an hour.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I came home with bloody fingers, because this is-- you know, to-- to fit a plastic, hard plastic, on that frame, was-- it was a hard job.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this was a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I made $29 a week after-- after deductions, because they deducted Social Security and something, they deducted from me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after several weeks, I couldn't take this job.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
